# Images Directory

This directory contains image assets for the Meal Generator Planner application.

## Structure
- `meal_placeholder.png` - Placeholder image for meals without photos
- `app_icon/` - Application icon variants
- `backgrounds/` - Background images for screens
- `icons/` - Custom icon assets

## Usage
Images are referenced in Flutter using:
```dart
Image.asset('assets/images/meal_placeholder.png')
```

## Optimization
- Use WebP format for better compression
- Provide multiple resolutions (1x, 2x, 3x)
- Compress images before adding to reduce app size